577
00:47:06,790 --> 00:47:10,055
<i>Yes, truly, a little bribe never hurts.</i>

578
00:47:10,594 --> 00:47:12,653
Well, thank you very much, Ralph.

579
00:47:18,101 --> 00:47:19,898
Merry Christmas.

580
00:47:22,639 --> 00:47:23,901
Happy New Year.

581
00:47:26,743 --> 00:47:28,802
You can take your seat now, Ralph.

582
00:47:52,402 --> 00:47:55,462
<i>The weeks of drinking gallons of Ovaltine,</i>
<i>in order to get...</i>

