00:48:34,778 --> 00:48:38,339
<i>Honors and benefits.</i>
<i>Already at the age of nine.</i>

595
00:48:44,187 --> 00:48:45,518
<i>Come on. Let's get on with it.</i>

596
00:48:45,589 --> 00:48:48,558
<i>I don't need all that jazz</i>
<i>about smugglers and pirates.</i>

597
00:48:49,593 --> 00:48:52,153
<i>Listen tomorrow night</i>
<i>for the concluding adventure of...</i>

