00:49:19,623 --> 00:49:22,387
<i>... 25. 14. 1 1. 18.</i>

608
00:49:23,460 --> 00:49:24,222
<i>16. 23...</i>

609
00:49:24,294 --> 00:49:25,989
<i>Pierre was in great voice tonight.</i>

610
00:49:26,063 --> 00:49:29,829
<i>I could tell that tonight's message</i>
